Insider Activity


Individual




Veronica M. Hagen



Ms. Veronica M. Hagen is Independent Director at American Water Works Co., Inc., Lead Independent Director at The Southern Co., Independent Director at Newmont Mining Corp., Independent Director at Newmont Mining Corp. of Canada Ltd., a Member at Economic Club of Chicago, a Member at The Chicago Network and a Member at The Committee of 200. She is on the Board of Directors at American Water Works Co., Inc., The Southern Co., AVINTIV Specialty Materials, Inc., AVINTIV, Inc., Newmont Mining Corp. and Newmont Mining Corp. of Canada Ltd. Ms. Hagen was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Sappi Fine Paper North America, President by Alcoa Engineered Products, Chief Customer Officer & Vice President by Alcoa, Inc., and Executive Vice President by Alumax, Inc. She also served on the board at Jacuzzi Brands, Inc. She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California.



