Veronica M. Hagen

Age : 71Public asset : 1,599,064 USDLinked companies :  Southern Co -  Newmont Mining Corp -  American Water Works Company Inc 





Summary 



Ms. Veronica M. Hagen is a Member at Economic Club of Chicago, a Member at The Chicago Network and a Member at The Committee of 200.She is on the Board of Directors at American Water Works Co., Inc., The Southern Co., AVINTIV, Inc. and Newmont Mining Corp. Ms. Hagen was previously employed as an Independent Director by Newmont Mining Corp. of Canada Ltd., President & Chief Executive Officer by Sappi Fine Paper North America, Inc, President by Alcoa Engineered Products, Chief Customer Officer & Vice President by Alcoa, Inc., and Executive Vice President by Alumax, Inc.She also served on the board at Polymer Group, Inc. and Jacuzzi Brands, Inc.She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California.



